main_body:
Regulation (EEC) No 2454/93 is amended as follows:
(1) Annex 48 is replaced by the text set out in Annex I to this Regulation;
(2) Annex 49 is replaced by the text set out in Annex II to this Regulation;
(3) Annex 50 is replaced by the text set out in Annex III to this Regulation;
(4) in Annex 51, in box 7, the text ‘Turkey,’ is inserted between the text ‘Switzerland,’ and ‘Andorra’;
(5) in Annex 51a, in box 6, the text ‘Turkey,’ is inserted between the text ‘Switzerland,’ and ‘Andorra’.
